Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How's work?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Rosemary doing well too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's made a lot of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And is she used to school--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-I apologize.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I have to get going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought with me a photo of Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you let me see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the day after tomorrow\Nat this restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:00:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've completely quit drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And my life's back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this might be the first time\NI'm living this properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've realized how much I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let her decide for herself\Nif she'll meet you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.59,0:02:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Another coffee, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, what kind of person\Ndo you think this man is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here to receive counseling from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you I'm no fortune-teller.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:04:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the result of many years\Nmeeting with your clients, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who discovered the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is the one\Nwho found Fahren's body first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They say he's just a friend though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, Richard.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Working is all fine and well,\Nbut you need some time to relax as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am taking it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Doctor…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be able to see my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I bet you're looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-However…\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you meet her,\Nyou cannot get back what was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,\Nyou must never touch any alcohol, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Going back to work after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How about finally facing head-on\Nthe incident that got you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,kicked out of the force?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's 17 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot him to death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,during work, while I was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use in trying to run from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot erase that truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's important is…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"To move forward\Nfrom that incident," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a pretty good student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get 100 out of 100?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't give perfect scores that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'd say\Nthose with a perfect score are boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-No way!\N-Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl Neuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Munich University's economics department,\Nbusiness management major.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Fahren, he told the prostitute\Nhe was Schuwald's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not yet confirmed\Nif this is true or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this young man\Nis somehow connected to this case…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard, the cleaning is done,\Nso I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks for your hard work, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't too hard at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A single man living alone\Nin such a tidy manner
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is no easy feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:08:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was an awful mess in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A photo of your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you got a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll get to meet her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, how nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be so happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Any daughter would be\Nhappy to see their parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,FRIEDRICH EMMANUEL SCHOOL\NOF MUNICH UNIVERSITY
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to turn in your report okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl Neuman…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you come forth to Schuwald\Nand say you are his son?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a swindler too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you the real deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If he really is Schuwald's son…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A parent always wants to meet their child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she doesn't want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. No, that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also quite busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to order something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go stay with Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you still want to meet him as an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But you mustn't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't resent him if he treats you coldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't resent him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This was from your dad\Nwhen you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"With no one to admire them,\NLares's daffodils flourish."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"With no one who cares,\Nthe trees of Paelia rustle."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, wheel tracks filled with the blood\Nof an unnamed walking man."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That was magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Neuman, you have become\Na magnificent reader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It is impressive that your Latin improved\Nso much in this short span of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually taking lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you have a talented teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's not just his Latin.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He has knowledge of law and economics…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he even understands philosophy\Nthat encompasses all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That young man is so perfect\Nthat it is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Mr. Schuwald…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A young man like him…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he were your real son?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Schuwald smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he thinks of you\Nas a suitable son for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I was jealous,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,even though it's clear\Nyou're more outstanding than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate myself for being jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell Schuwald\Nthat you are his real son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said from the start\Nthat that's not my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I did tell him,\Nhe'd never believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but he'd only see me\Nas one of the hyenas after his fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The life my mother lived before she died…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The feelings I've had living until now…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know all that.\NI don't want him to think of me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you should tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he'll know\Nthe truth about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't believe anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you have something\Nthat'll make him believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:15:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that will make him believe\Nthat you are his real son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to remember.\NThere should be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you. There's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't plan to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you learning\NLatin from me like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you want to make him happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you want him to like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of quitting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the reading job at his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to quit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan, I'll say this only to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I do own something that can act as proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't plan to shove it in his face\Nand say I'm his real son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My foster parents\Nare coming to see me next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens, I'll…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to make sure\Nyour resolve doesn't waver,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe it's best I hold onto\Nthat piece of evidence for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved you look so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we were worried about\Nwhether you're eating properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm being careful, since eating out\Nwill actually make me gain more weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom's food makes you gain weight too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How's university?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you made friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have a good friend\NI can talk to about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell things are going well\Njust by looking at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly thankful\NI get to study like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone from one foster home\Nto another until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but you two treated me so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're such a wonderful boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Mr. Lindner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you stop calling me\NMr. Lindner now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you thought about\Nour offer to adopt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to college\Nand asked us to wait a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but we thought maybe it's finally time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe in us as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:18:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your real mother and father\Nmay be alive somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what we do,\Nwe may never be your real parents, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you two are my real mom and dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll splurge on some nice wine today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, could we get the wine menu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a special day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Neuman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:19:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you're planning on\Nquitting the part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You did your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a good job\Nin improving your Latin that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It truly is a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll truly miss having you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're okay with it,\Ncould you read for me one last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd be happy to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How about section three\Nof From Aeolis to Lemnos?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"That mysterious ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,desires death for even the god Apollo."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Just like Cerberus, its only amusement\Nis wishing for the death
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,of sons and daughters."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"'Now, go forth,' Zeus whispers."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"He says, 'Go forth. Go forth.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dance at the temples\Nof the dispirited gods."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh gods of Juno who reside in\Nthe sea, on earth, and in the heavens."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Go to Mount Parthenion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and steal the forbidden apple\Nof Campania."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"All shall come here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which my heart seeks…"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"And that which…"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Schuwald, that phone call just now…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the most pleasant reading\NI've ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you hide this until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe this is the rabbit's foot\Nthat I gave to your mother, Margot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a charm that was to give\Nyou good luck once you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This belongs to you, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've put you through so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is thanks to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He will now work under me as my secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a young man I can trust.
